    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Prerequisite</strong>: Reality Marble Genjutsu pledge</p><hr /><p>When you are in an area with Dim light or Darkness, you can use your action to become invisible. While Invisible in this way you do not make sounds when you move. You lose the benefit of this mirage when you move more than half your movement speed in a single round, attack, or cast a jutsu.</p>",
